text: real chivit teangoasa nung phloksa rosacheate nei kar slab . haey pitabrakd nasa a l laoh nung tabasnang nouv phalbony teang lay robsa puok anak nea thngai barlok . dau che neah anaknea haey del trauv a l laoh banhchiesa pi phleung nork ning ban banhchoul ke tow knong thansuokr noh ke brakadchea ttuol ban chokchy . haey karorsanow knong lokey nih kmeanoavei krawpi kar te r k traaeal baokabanhchhot noh laey
